    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Heap bytes used",
      "description": "Kernel-heap occupancy from `Heap::used()` \u2014 sum of alignment-padded `layout.size()` across live allocations. Excludes hole-list metadata, so slightly undercounts unavailable bytes. Out of a 4 MiB region.",
