      "description": "Monotonic counter \u2014 every GlobalAlloc::alloc that returned null. Healthy kernel: 0. A non-zero value means the heap is out of space \u2014 bump HEAP_FRAMES or implement growable heap (strategy (b) in the step-4 plan).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
